=== Portable Winterizer ===
The '''"Portable Winterizer"''' was the first consumable item that was available for purchase with VRChat Credits. On December 10, 2025, the item was changed to be a permanent, infinite use item instead of a consumable, after community feedback was taken into consideration.<ref>[https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202542p1 VRChat 2025.4.2p1] on ''[https://docs.vrchat.com docs.vrchat.com]''. Dated December 10, 2025. Retrieved December 10, 2025.</ref>

Users that purchased, or were gifted, the "Portable Winterizer" were granted a non-consumable version of the item. The consumable version of the item is still available in user's inventories.
